At the regional level, coverage of OST among PWID was highest in south Asia (82 OST clients per 100 PWID, UI 67–greater than parity) and western Europe (64, 46–95; 
 table 3). Globally, there are 16 (UI 11–25) OST recipients per 100 PWID. Coverage increased somewhat using the denominator of primary opioid injectors; we estimated that there are 19 (UI 13–31) OST recipients per 100 primary opioid injectors (
 table 3).
